Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安   日安\N某私立大学学生   结衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.92,0:00:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.99,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是大学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学生   女校大学生\N女校大学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女子大学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.00,0:00:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.26,0:00:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是校花吗  不是\N不是   对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.80,0:00:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.54,0:00:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有在打工吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.61,0:00:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有在兼家教的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭 教师啊\N家教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.48,0:00:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.29,0:01:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭教师应该很辛苦吧\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.62,0:01:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家教有很多困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为学生是男生\N男生所以....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.24,0:01:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被用奇怪的眼光看\N奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.18,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是很辛辣的老师吧\N或许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.32,0:01:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也有个男生在看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.59,0:01:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.79,0:01:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.32,0:01:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不要像这样打扮\N会比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.46,0:01:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎样的打扮比较好呢\N大概两千日币以下左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.34,0:01:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要\N那样有点..对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.34,0:01:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你使用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.75,0:02:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在不会被发现的地方\N来观察学生   我想会有一此信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.63,0:02:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗   我努力看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.44,0:02:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体内射精的教学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.99,0:02:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁学生去厕所时\N放置摄影机的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小广   接下来继续刚刚的\N话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.63,0:03:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是某某先生的文章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.97,0:03:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有关接下来会成长\N的一篇文章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.11,0:03:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关民主的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.98,0:03:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请写下两个主要的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.79,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是为了民主的运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有关基督教的运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.66,0:03:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从江户时代\N持续下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗   小广
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.14,0:04:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你确认一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.15,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.31,0:04:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关现在男性的问题\N男性的问题喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.44,0:04:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去问题会减少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有关问题的产生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.52,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关秋天的时候\N有关天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会怎样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的东西的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在墙上乱画的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关一切的发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是有什么的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.21,0:05:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关一切的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样有的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.69,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好听吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.96,0:05:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能集中吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.44,0:05:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，休息一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.65,0:05:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去厕所\N好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.28,0:06:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着拿着摄影机\N诱惑学生的影片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被发现吗\N对   没被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我确定一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊\N有一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.51,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点危险\N有一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这或许就是老师的意志吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.39,0:07:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N老师拍过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏摄影机的确认\N是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.81,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷的在看着老师的\N样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在数什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.82,0:07:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师有很黄的样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且裙子很短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.83,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有打算这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有理由吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:08:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有男朋友也没有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个\N那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.38,0:08:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟之前说的一样\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试看看做个爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.92,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看吧\N不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服喔\N不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.79,0:08:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样...\N他也很想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.74,0:08:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师不想的原因或许是\N因为是学生的关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个小时就好\N这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.88,0:08:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧\N不知道老师的心情是....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许可以也说不定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.62,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧\N或许可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.89,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想或许是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.16,0:08:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与老师约在旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合吗\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N很害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您在当老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在当老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.26,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听过跟学生做过的老师吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.07,0:09:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没听过\N有点困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的   对\N等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.82,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想过很色的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊\N好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有被喜欢吧\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个姿色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常来吗\N不常来   是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.99,0:10:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办\N从胸部开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次吗    从胸部吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好好看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.34,0:10:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心痒痒的吗\N心痒痒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此    对\N我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.28,0:10:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看老师色的样子\N可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗     来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把舌头伸出来让我看\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变色了  知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒\N喜欢哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.76,0:12:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳头  乳头   真的啊\N我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌头伸出来那样也很\N色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.84,0:12:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.12,0:12:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.33,0:12:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.06,0:12:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很害羞吗\N害羞   摄影机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗    好害羞\N是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.08,0:13:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这    完全被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被舔过耳朵吗\N既然来了就....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢耳朵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.84,0:13:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有摸到
