Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.25,0:42:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.46,0:42:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.73,0:42:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.22,0:43:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个脸好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.96,0:43:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多精子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.63,0:43:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾到脸吧\N好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.77,0:43:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.77,0:43:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射射你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.51,0:43:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后又放到隐藏的地方\N回到教书的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.19,0:43:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后是以民主自由为基础
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.86,0:44:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后是以这样为进步的
