Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.35,0:44:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:22.62,0:44:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就分裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.69,0:44:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.36,0:44:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了\N小广
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:39.30,0:44:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小广\N念书不能集中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.31,0:44:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:49.98,0:44:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样说
