Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.67,0:45:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托小广
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:32.02,0:45:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是偶尔的教书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:36.96,0:45:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你舒服喔
