Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:55.25,0:46:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都想摸老师的胸部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.77,0:46:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以喔
