Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:17.75,0:54:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.30,0:54:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定可以集中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.85,0:54:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上老师就把影片\N交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:04.86,0:55:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真不错
