Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:07.33,0:56:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:11.86,0:56:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在而已吧
