Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:42.48,1:08:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:45.55,1:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说之前\N我很烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:02.63,1:09:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:08.64,1:09:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想做更色的事情吗
